<entry valign="middle" align="center">Length</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">Mass</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">Capacity</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row valign="top">
<entry valign="middle" align="left">1 kilometer (km) = 1,000 m<newline/><newline/>
1 hectometer (hm) = 100 m<newline/><newline/>
1 dekameter (dam) = 10 m<newline/><newline/>
