1 decimeter (dm) = 0.1 m<newline/><newline/>
1 centimeter (cm) = 0.01 m<newline/><newline/>
1 millimeter (mm) = 0.001 m</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">1 kilogram (kg) = 1,000 g<newline/><newline/>
1 hectogram (hg) = 100 g<newline/><newline/>
1 dekagram (dag) = 10 g<newline/><newline/>
1 gram (g) = 1 g<newline/><newline/>
1 decigram (dg) = 0.1 g<newline/><newline/>
