<para id="fs-id1170653893032"><link target-id="CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_01_10_008"/> shows how inches and centimeters are related on a ruler.</para>
<figure id="CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_01_10_008">
<media id="fs-id1170654009196" alt="A ruler with inches and centimeters.">
